OL,3,CScores on the doors ratings for care
OL,4,Chomes in Wales
OL,6,FCare services in Wales will now have
OL,7,Fto display their inspection rating to
OL,8,Fhelp residents and their families make
OL,9,Finformed decisions.
OL,11,FThe new rules start on April 1st, and
OL,12,Fmean care homes and domiciliary
OL,13,Fsupport services will have to to
OL,14,Fdisplay their rating at their premises
OL,15,Fand online, following an inspection.
OL,17,FThe ratings will be split into four
OL,18,Fareas: Well-being; Care and Support;
OL,19,FLeadership and Management; Environment.
