OL,4,Chomes in Wales
OL,6,FEach one will be marked as excellent,
OL,7,Fgood, requires improvement or requires
OL,8,Fsignificant improvement.
OL,10,FOver the coming months, more and more
OL,11,Fservices will be displaying their
OL,12,Fratings, however it will take up to
OL,13,Ftwo years for all services to be
OL,14,Fsigned up.
OL,16,FMinister for Children and Social Care,
OL,17,FDawn Bowden said:
