OL,3,CScores on the doors ratings for care
OL,4,Chomes in Wales
OL,6,F"Care services throughout Wales have a
OL,7,Fcrucial role in looking after people.
OL,8,FFor many of them, a care service can
OL,9,Falso be their home, where they live
OL,10,Fand thrive, and we want to keep
OL,11,Fensuring they receive the best
OL,12,Fpossible care.
OL,14,F"These ratings will enable people to
OL,15,Fmake important decisions in choosing
OL,16,Fwhat's right for them and support
OL,17,Ftheir well-being."
